credit. Underwriting losses, however, rose from IPounds 1.34m to IPounds
2.54m as a result of severe weather claims and increased large public
liability claims.
Group earnings per share were almost doubled at 18.5p (9.6p), and the
interim dividend is raised to 3.5p (3.3p).
