<HEADLINE>
FT  10 AUG 93 / People: Cookson
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Richard Malthouse, previously group secretary of Del Monte Foods
International, has been appointed group secretary at COOKSON on the
resignation of Tim Ware.
</TEXT>
